<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="118" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d118">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1" type="to">Stalin</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d118fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché, Moscow, via the White
                                House Map Room and Navy channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">operational priority</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Aboard
                                        the</hi> U. S. S. “<hi rend="smallcaps">Iowa</hi>”</placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-12">12 November 1943</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Personal and secret for Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1">Stalin</persName> from the President.</p>
                        <p>I am of course made very happy by your telegram of ten November<note n="2" xml:id="d118fn2"><hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_78">p. 78</ref>.</note> and the definite prospect of
                            our meeting, and I shall be very glad to see Mr. <persName corresp="#p_MVM1">Molotov</persName> in Cairo on the twenty-second.
                            I am just leaving for French North Africa. Warm regards.</p>
                        <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_RFD1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>